# Raw Data & Retrieval Scope (AGENTS.md §4)

Raw path layout: `data/raw/{project}/{build}/{type}/<file>`

| Segment | Path | Meaning |
|---------|------|---------|
| `global` | `data/raw/global/` | Enterprise shared (`project=global`, `build=global`) |
| `common` | `data/raw/{project}/common/` | All builds in that project |
| `{build}` | e.g. `p1` | Specific hardware build |

Folders `note`, `sch`, `sop`, `datasheet` → `document_type` via `config/default.yaml` → `data_layout.document_type_folders`.

## Ingestion

- Derive `project`, `build`, `document_type` from path — never hardcode project names in `src/`.
- Write to `data/processed/` mirroring `data/raw/` (`.md` + optional `.meta.json`).
- Use metadata field `build`, never `board`.

## Retrieval

- Honor `retrieval.scope_inheritance` (default `true`).
- Filter `project=X, build=Y` → also search `X/common/` and `global/`.
- Rank: build-specific > `common` > `global`.

## V1 formats

PDF, Markdown, TXT, Excel only. Skip `.key` / `.numbers` with a clear log until parsers exist.

Full detail: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) §4, [README.md](../../README.md#raw-data-layout).
